description: Performs TrackSOM (cluster n=15) and views the results with a heatmap and minimum spanning tree (MST). TrackSOM clusters are also visualized in a heatmap using MEM score. 2D plot with Flt-SNE and UMAP. Downsampling filter applied (1%).  For use with the FlowJo plugin uploaded data.
name: FlowJo Cluster Explorer #3 - TrackSOM
